OL,3,CReeves denies UK on path to austerity
OL,4,Cas she confirms 15% Civil Service cuts
OL,6,FRachel Reeves has denied that Labour
OL,7,Fis heading towards austerity as she
OL,8,Fconfirmed plans to cut Civil Service
OL,9,Frunning costs by 15%.
