OL,3,CReeves denies UK on path to austerity
OL,4,Cas she confirms 15% Civil Service cuts
OL,6,FAt the same time, she said Labour was
OL,7,Flooking to cut back the Civil Service,
OL,8,Fwhich she said had swelled during the
OL,9,FCovid-19 pandemic, by slashing its
OL,10,F"back office functions, the
OL,11,Fadministrative and bureaucracy
OL,12,Ffunctions" by the end of this
OL,13,Fparliament.
OL,15,FIt comes after a backlash, including
OL,16,Fin the party's own ranks, to cuts to
OL,17,Fwelfare spending and a decision to
OL,18,Fslash the aid budget to fund a boost
OL,19,Fto defence spending, and ahead of the
OL,20,FChancellor's spring statement on
OL,21,FWednesday.
