OL,12,FKuenssberg: "Last year, I put #100
OL,13,Fbillion more into capital spending
OL,14,Fthan the previous government had
OL,15,Fcommitted to, we put more than #20
OL,16,Fbillion into the National Health
OL,17,FService.
OL,19,F"That is a far cry from what we've
OL,20,Fseen under Conservative governments in
OL,21,Fthe last 14 years."
